      "comment": "LAKEVIEW HUNTER (6) has a strong winning strike-rate here having won two of three starts. In the money last time at Sandown (42.31) in a Special conditions race, finishing a 14 length third. Expected to go close. CHARLESTOWN (1) made light work of a wide draw last time with a slick early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing second (42.27) at Sandown over 715m. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Must be included in calculations. IRISH MILLIE (3) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Slick Nitro (42.93) in a Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to her credit. Must be included in calculations. PASS MARK (2) must be among the chances on the last run here.",
